{"tid":2106444,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【武漢肺炎】HKTVMall推在家工作計劃 「三聲內要接電話」Son姐：侮辱員工 慘過坐監","createTime":"2020-07-13T10:39:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-13T11:45:40.000Z","uid":78546,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"da341049f5a25f344e0a31e4444b431d3c11da56","tid":2106444,"uid":78546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T10:39:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20200713/FEKFLQILWDRPGHJDDBYLQRZ72I/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200713%2FFEKFLQILWDRPGHJDDBYLQRZ72I%2F&d=luXbQZY1AauiUI8MFdBmxAfwWQc8qO99IFO6%2BGFOovI%3D&h=8523000c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200713%2FFEKFLQILWDRPGHJDDBYLQRZ72I%2F&h=bf41ccd5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20200713/FEKFLQILWDRPGHJDDBYLQRZ72I/</a> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n資深獵頭人張慧敏（Son姐）看過HKTVMall電郵後，向記者炮轟，該公司此舉明顯反映對員工的不信任，「我覺得好苛刻，係侮辱員工、慘過坐監。」<br />\n<br />\nSon姐指，政策原意是希望減低受感染的機會，「講到全日要stand by，如果屋企小朋友同老人家唔舒服，係唔係唔陪得去得睇醫生？點為之全日？咁我訓教時使唔使三聲內接電話？如果我當時同客傾緊生意呢？」<br />\n<br />\n她續指，「坐監都有得放飯啦」，指星期六、日都不能出街，「set出嚟係唔係鼓勵員工唔好揀？揀返工返完我都仲可以自由。」"},{"pid":"7eeca6a930dd30862e2b084b0f22772946319bea","tid":2106444,"uid":358190,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T11:45:40.000Z","msg":"呢條友成日串柒柒，今次竟然企員工果邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}